As time progressed I begun to search more, became an edgy Stalinist and begun exploring my ideas about Race, Religion and the Jews. field_12:
You're probably here wondering "What the fuck is a technofascist?" It's because I strongly support Oswald Mosely's beliefs desire for "the union of government with science," or as he put it, even more directly, "Our whole future depends on science, and we should never forget it for one moment." It's technology, not democracy, which has increasingly driven the advances of humanity and the human condition of late, and that will only continue in future.

More broadly, I generally agree with Mosely in a number of other areas, e.g. “The Fascist principle is liberty in private, obligation in public. In his public capacity a man must behave as befits a citizen and a member of the State; his actions must conform to the interests of the State, which protects and governs him and guarantees his personal freedom. In private he may behave as he likes." He was also largely unconcerned with racism or anti-Semitism, beliefs which have held Fascism back for decades, by tying public perception of it to the abject failures of the Nazis.

To succeed, fascism must abandon concepts and conceits that were relevant only to an earlier time. All fascism is a product of its era and location, and we need an ideology that looks forward, not one gazing back to, and philosophically stuck in, the Weimar Republic.

[And in case you're wondering, my location comes from a pejorative label, thrown at me by Nebuchadnezzar II. I've no clue at all what it means, but it's a marvelous turn of phrase well worth preserving. My member title was similarly bestowed upon me by a wonderful mod...]

field_12:
Taken From My Introduction

I'll start off by saying that I live in the United States Boston, Massachusetts. A 30 year old male that is a full-time armed security guard, won't give too much information of the company and place I work for security reasons. Unfortunately, a work place has little tolerance for a belief system that is absolutely demonized and it could possibly trace back. How? I don't know, can never be too careful. Anyways, as most would know that live in the states that MA is about as liberal as California, strict gun laws, safespaces, LBQT + SJW friendly, all things problematic.  I don't have to get into the list of things wrong with the country, and what it would take to repair years and centuries worth of damage. I am a firm believer of National Socialism, I can differentiate the differences between Fascism and National Socialism, what I would like to find here is extensive knowledge in our line of politics. I'm not one of those people that cherry picks and polyqueers a political idea mashing them together to make one unicorn government that works for everyone. NO, that's not what I'm looking for at all. I've read some of the subjects on the forum, I even had a friend on here that showed me a thread on White Monger's introduction. And that is exactly the type of people I want to avoid, if you're going to be a Fascist, be a Fascist and follow all the way through with it. If you're going to be NS, same deal go all the way with it or bust.  What I like about National Socialism and why it's been a huge success in Germany, and why the globalist Jews are scared of it. It's an idea that works, the National is the country itself, the socialist is the people of the country.  The people of the country comes first, above all no exceptions.  I have some PDFs on National Socialism, including Gottfried Feder's "Manifesto for the Abolition of Interest-Slavery (1919)" and recently got into reading another one of his, "The German State on a National and Socialist Foundation".  I'll admit that I am not a "know it all" and I'm not coming with a "know it all" attitude, I come to this site to step away from "dank redpilling memes" and whatever this generation is into these days.  I've come to speak with like minded folks that have vast knowledge, everyone has different ideas and thoughts in which I am open to all of them.  If it's knowledge that is against the interest of our enemies, I'll take it and utilize it. I know what most of you do and say to lowbies, but go ahead and throw in your worst criticisms.  I am very thick skinned, and this does come with my profession of dealing with people. I'm not at all a stranger of being roasted. Words wouldn't stop me from seeking the greatest knowledge.

I do have other interests, I'm an absolute gun maniac, I'm trying to hit the firing range more.  My biggest interest as of now, is a specific group that have recently attacked the universities in my state with propaganda fliers, the Atomwaffen. I know little about them, but I appreciate what they have done even though they have to do things under the radar.  In MA anyway, because our law enforcement is absolutely strict. Seeing the fear from the delicate left, it put a smile on my face. All because they've seen a piece of paper with words on it, it frightens them. Especially with words that doesn't coorelate with their ideals, but it comes to show you how defenseless they really are. My other biggest fascinations are Guerilla Warfare, and shadow militia fanatic groups, especially when it comes to NS for some reason it tickles me.  And whenever I try to bring up the subject of guerilla warfare, some people are quick to label me as "edgy" or "LARPer" which is not the case. Then I have to apologize to the nay sayers that politics isn't puppies and rainbows, especially National Socialism.. Anyway getting sidetracked, there isn't really a movement in MA that I know of. I don't know how many members of Atomwaffen are in MA, but I'd like to get in contact I do have skills that I would discuss privately. We had a "movement" before, but they split up from in house fighting and narcotic drug overdoses.. In conclusion, I'm here to distance myself from the NatSoc anime fanbase that flood Facebook with pepe meme nonsense, in order to have a series of discussions with actual intellectuals.
